description: Demolition of existing buildings and construction of seven buildings, rising from 7 storeys up to 16 storeys to provide 419 new dwellings, 656m of Class B1 (Business) floorspace, 225m of either Class B1 and/or D1 (non-residential institution) floorspace, 330m of Class A1 (shop) floorspace, a health clinic (1,907m), and a day nursery (367m), 183 parking spaces and landscaping.
